# Project Profile
- Stack: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Track: Frontend AI Engineering (FlyRank Internship Capstone)

# AI Behavior Rules
- Always use TypeScript with explicit types; avoid using 'any'.
- Write clean, functional React components with proper modularization.
- Follow Tailwind CSS best practices and avoid redundant utility classes.

# Commit Standards
- Whenever suggesting git actions, always enforce the Conventional Commits 1.0.0 specification.